<BR>
As for a necros place in high level groups, sure much of their duties involve being mana batteries. But hey, then clerics are health batteries, and wizards are just damage batteries. You can make the job of any class seem unimportant and unpleasant. Also, lifetaps are the LEAST RESISTED spells in the game, and the taunt isn't too much worse than a normal damage spell. Also, necros get the 2nd best, very close to the best, pets in the game, and eventually get UNFEARABLE PETS! Besides, without mana in a high level group or raid, what would you be? One word... SCREWED!!!!!!!!!
